{"tid":1139312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵：已就乘客阻礙列車車門關閉事件報警","createTime":"2019-05-05T07:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T07:20:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6287d68b7c636bba4985b36d2c599fba245624b","tid":1139312,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港鐵指已就有乘客阻礙列車車門關閉事件報警。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳片段，一名男子在樂富站以身體阻擋車門及月台幕門關閉，又曾多次踢向車門。港鐵職員到場要求他離開，但他拒絕，並向職員謾罵。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵證實上周五晚約十時，觀塘綫一列往黃埔的列車駛至樂富站時，車長收到訊號，顯示列車車門及月台幕門未能正常運作，於是派職員到場了解。<br />\n<br />\n期間一名男子阻礙職員登車，車務控制中心隨即安排石硤尾站及太子站職員了解事件及報警，職員與男子最終於旺角站下車，事件交由警方處理。<br />\n<br />\n至於網上流傳另一條有人強行打開車門的片段，港鐵說不清楚來源及拍攝時間。<br />\n<br />\n根據車站紀錄，這數天未有收到有乘客反映有關情況。"},{"pid":"d9660aa7122fcce0aa4a49708152dc0051c16700","tid":1139312,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=346878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346878&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2yzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=03e62334\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346878&h=057da54a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=346878</a>"},{"pid":"ecc2ed7b372a6c88bb0af35ee32957cad1e8f490","tid":1139312,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"碌柒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbca1205883a9efd1f42ac7c63ff2f781d319fc","tid":1139312,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:20:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=49&amp;v=7Lq4LLb-P6A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D49%26v%3D7Lq4LLb-P6A&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2yzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=d1cb4653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=49&amp;v=7Lq4LLb-P6A</a>"}]}